-- BC Partners to acquire PetSmart for $8.7 billion
-- By Greg Roumeliotis in New York
-- Sun Dec 14, 2014 04:31PM EST
-- None



Dec 14 (Reuters) - Pet supply retailer PetSmart Inc <PETM.N> said on Sunday it had agreed to sell itself to a private equity consortium led by BC Partners Ltd for $8.7 billion, in the largest leveraged buyout of the year.

